        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="啊"><a href="#啊" class="headerlink" title="啊"></a>啊</h1><h2 id="啊啊"><a href="#啊啊" class="headerlink" title="啊啊"></a>啊啊</h2><h3 id="啊啊啊"><a href="#啊啊啊" class="headerlink" title="啊啊啊"></a>啊啊啊</h3><h4 id="啊啊啊啊"><a href="#啊啊啊啊" class="headerlink" title="啊啊啊啊"></a>啊啊啊啊</h4><h5 id="啊啊啊啊啊"><a href="#啊啊啊啊啊" class="headerlink" title="啊啊啊啊啊"></a>啊啊啊啊啊</h5><h6 id="啊啊啊啊啊啊"><a href="#啊啊啊啊啊啊" class="headerlink" title="啊啊啊啊啊啊"></a>啊啊啊啊啊啊</h6><hr><p><strong>粗体</strong>细体</p><p><em>斜体</em>     不斜体</p><p><em><strong>又粗又斜</strong></em></p><p><del>划去</del>不划去</p><blockquote><p>这是引用</p><blockquote><p>引用套引用</p></blockquote></blockquote><ul><li>list<ul><li>ee</li><li>eee</li></ul></li><li>e</li><li>e</li></ul><ol><li>aaa</li><li>aaaa</li><li>aaaaa</li></ol><p>$f(x)&#x3D;2x^6+3x_6+\Delta+\sqrt3$</p><p>$$f(x居中独立)$$</p><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">printf</span>(<span class="string">&quot;yyy&quot;</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><table><thead><tr><th align="center">分隔</th><th>分割</th><th align="center">分格</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td align="center">aaa</td><td>aa</td><td align="center">a</td></tr></tbody></table><p><a href="https://userenity.github.io/">blog</a></p><p><img src="https://picture.gptkong.com/20240805/152246d75026264c2a8e6a13630051f190.png" alt="我鸭的英姿"></p>]]></content>
      
      
